          </li>
          <li class="nav-item active" role="presentation">
            <a class="nav-link" id="contact-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabb5" role="tab" aria-controls="contact"
              aria-selected="false">Refund</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-7">
        <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
          <div class="tab-pane active" id="tabb1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="home-tab">
            <h3 class="faq__slide-title">How to Place an Order with SMMFansGrow </h3>
            <p class="faq__slide-text">Placing an order for fast, affordable, high quality social engagements and social proof is quick and
              easy. </p>

            <p class="red-txt">Step 1: <span class="blue-txt">Create an Account </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 2: <span class="blue-txt">Login to your dashboard </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 3: <span class="blue-txt">Select the platform you need marketing help with </span>
            </p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 4: <span class="blue-txt">Select the social media marketing service you need </span>
            </p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 5: <span class="blue-txt">Enter payment instruction and check in later to track your
                order status.</span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabb2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="profile-tab">
            <h3 class="faq__slide-title">How to Pay for Orders </h3>
            <p class="faq__slide-text">After you have created an account, just follow the steps below to set your account payment correctly. You
              only need to set it up once and you can order as many times as you want after.</p>

            <p class="red-txt">Step 1: <span class="blue-txt">Login to your dashboard </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 2: <span class="blue-txt">Select payment details </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 3: <span class="blue-txt">Select payment option and enter your details.</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 4: <span class="blue-txt">Select a service and click the order button</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 5: <span class="blue-txt">Confirm payment </span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabb3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="contact-tab">
            <h3 class="faq__slide-title">How to Open A Customer Support Ticket </h3>
            <p class="faq__slide-text">If you have any questions or encounter any problems with your order, our Customer Service Ticket system
              has you all covered.</p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 1: <span class="blue-txt">Login to your dashboard </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 2: <span class="blue-txt">Select Customer Support </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 3: <span class="blue-txt">Click Create Ticket</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 4: <span class="blue-txt">Enter the details of your request</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 5: <span class="blue-txt">Answer our response email</span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabb4" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="contact-tab">
            <h3 class="faq__slide-title">How to Get Child Panel Support</h3>
            <p class="faq__slide-text">If you have any questions or encounter any problems with our Child Panel system, we will take care of
              you.</p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 1: <span class="blue-txt">Login to your dashboard </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 2: <span class="blue-txt">Select Customer Support </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 3: <span class="blue-txt">Click Create Ticket</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 4: <span class="blue-txt">Enter the details of your request – make sure to mention
                Child Panel support</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 5: <span class="blue-txt">Answer our response email</span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabb5" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="contact-tab">
            <h3 class="faq__slide-title">How to Get a Refund</h3>
            <p class="faq__slide-text">If you want a refund for the undelivered portion of your order, we’ve made getting your money back quick
              and easy</p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 1: <span class="blue-txt">Login to your dashboard </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 2: <span class="blue-txt">Select Customer Support </span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 3: <span class="blue-txt">Click Create Ticket</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 4: <span class="blue-txt">Enter the details of your refund request</span></p>
            <p class="red-txt">Step 5: <span class="blue-txt">Answer our response email</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

